    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Almandine that is cabochon-cut (a rounded, convex polished surface) and deep red in color. Its base is often hollowed to lighten its color. May display a four-rayed asterism (star-shaped), if rutile needles are included in the almandine.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
